### Prerequisites:

- Before requesting a device addition, please ensure there is not already a request for the device among the open issues.
- Make sure your Homey is upgraded to firmware v5 or higher.
- You need a physical example of the device.

### Device Information

- Device Name: `Zigbee Smart IR Remote`
- Device Model: `TS1201`
- Device Description: `Learnable Zigbee-based IR remote. For learning IR commands from IR devices and making them controllable through Zigbee.`
- Link to device image: [[Provide the URL to an image/photo of the device](https://www.url-to-images.com)](https://ae-pic-a1.aliexpress-media.com/kf/S12acfa44157144968a26ab1c515bf7bee.jpg_960x960q75.jpg_.avif)

